data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4-bedroom, 2-bath Single Family Home, nestled within the serene and gated community of Sereno. Skip the construction delays, as this home is move-in ready! Over 1800 sq. ft. of Florida Living, this residence features tile flooring throughout its main living areas. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the open-concept living and dinning room creating an inviting space to welcome family and friends. Property comes fully fenced, it has a water softener and storage racks on the garage. Sereno's gated community has NO CDD,  providing access to 2 delightful community pools and a playground. The location is highly advantageous, situated close to Hwy 17-92, Poinciana Parkway, and I-4. Additionally a new supermarket, High School, and Mater Academy, adding further appeal to the neighborhood. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, investor, or seeking a second home, this property is a gem not to be missed. Secure your private showing today and make this Home your own!
